type: software
title: "rbf-nonlocal-balance"
abstract: >-
  A meshless radial basis function (RBF) + BDF solver for nonlocal balance
  equations on irregular two-dimensional domains, implementing the numerical
  scheme of Melouani, Bouhamidi and El Harraki (2025).
authors:
