date-released: "2025-01-01"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/yassinemelouani/rbf-nonlocal-balance"
keywords:
  - radial basis functions
  - meshless methods
  - nonlocal balance equations
  - BDF time stepping
  - Newton-Krylov
  - hyper-viscosity

